definitions.definition: A market town and community with a town council in Carmarthenshire , Wales ( OS grid ref SN7634 ) .

main_definition: A market town and community with a town council in Carmarthenshire , Wales ( OS grid ref SN7634 ) .

definitions.definition: A geological epoch within the Silurian period from about 443 to 428 million years ago; marked by the appearance of the trilobites .

main_definition: ( geology ) A geological epoch within the Silurian period from about 443 to 428 million years ago; marked by the appearance of the trilobites .
